黑貓是無政府工團主義的象徵，不過一般無政府主義運動也可能用到它<ref>{{cite book|title=About cats|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=EtVvAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT67|author=Nicolae Sfetcu|year=2014|accessdate=2020-07-19|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719132905/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=EtVvAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT67|dead-url=no}}</ref>。牠的形象一般是張牙露爪，一邊弓腰一邊看似發出「嘶嘶」的聲音<ref>{{cite book|title=Keep the Wretches in Order: America's Biggest Mass Trial, the Rise of the Justice Department, and the Fall of the IWW|page=17|author=Dean Strang|publisher=University of Wisconsin Pres|isbn=9780299323301|year=3019|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5oCWDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA17|access-date=2020-07-19|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719204530/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5oCWDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此一象徵為世界产业工人的拉爾夫·卓別林（Ralph Chaplin）首創，寓意僱主看到他們「会倒一點霉」<ref>{{cite book|title=Partisans and Poets: The Political Work of American Poetry in the Great War|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=_nIkCcLM5yQC&pg=PA89|year=1997|publisher=Cambridge University Press|author=Mark W. van Wienen|isbn=9780521563963|page=89|access-date=2020-07-19|archive-date=2020-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200719180442/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=_nIkCcLM5yQC&pg=PA89|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

